              >
                Each demo takes just a few minutes but will show you training
                capabilities that didn't exist before. Pick the one that
                interests you most, or try them all.
              </p>

              <div
                class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center mb-6"
              >
                <Button
                  size="lg"
                  className="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-purple-600 hover:from-purple-400 hover:to-purple-500 text-white px-10 py-5 text-base font-bold rounded-full transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300"
